  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"A weakling like you could never win!\"</em></p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>You are always trying to win, whether it be in a fight to the death or in a children's card game. You have a number of d4s equal to your prof. bonus that you can add to any to hit roll or any saving throw.</p><h5 id=\"negative\">Negative</h5><p>When you feel like you're going to lose you start to lose your balance and start performing much worse than normal. When you are below 50% Hp You roll a d4 and subtract half the result from your to hit and saving throws.</p>",
